Orchard Sophia condo at Sophia Road by DB2Land

Freehold condo short walk from Dhoby Ghaut MRT and Plaza Singapura
Introducing Orchard Sophia, constructed at the core central region, where you can experience truly refined living with convenience and exclusivity blended in perfect harmony.
This elegant freehold residential haven is located just at the intersection of Sophia Road and Orchard Road in District 9, and it stands as the epitome of luxury and sophistication, giving true meaning to urban living in Singapore.

DB2land was established in 2006 and has been one of the most prominent figures in the property developing industry in Singapore.
The company today has a reach beyond the country and has successfully achieved regional developments in Malaysia.
Read More

In Closing

Orchard Sophia is a freehold residential gem that takes fine living and convenience to the next level.
With one of the most competitive price ranges you can buy into today, homeowners are lucky to have all the numerous buildings and near amenities in store for them.

Orchard Sophia FAQs

What is the address for Orchard Sophia?
The address for Orchard Sophia is 128 Sophia Road Singapore 228184 130 Sophia Road Singapore 228185.
What is the nearest MRT to Orchard Sophia?
The nearest MRT to Orchard Sophia is Dhoby Ghaut MRT Station.
How can I view Orchard Sophia's showflat?
Simply click here or give us a call at our sales hotline at +6561009876 to book a showflat appointment.
When is the TOP date for Orchard Sophia?
The expected TOP (Temporary Occupation Permit) date for Orchard Sophia is expected to be on 1Q 2027.
Who is the developer of Orchard Sophia?
Orchard Sophia Pte. Ltd. (a subsidiary of DB2Land) is the developer for Orchard Sophia.
What is the tenure for Orchard Sophia?
The Tenure for Orchard Sophia is Freehold (Estate In Fee Simple).
How many units are there in Orchard Sophia?
There are 78 residential units in Orchard Sophia.
What are the units mix for Orchard Sophia?
The units in Orchard Sophia are comprised of 15 x 1 Bedroom units, 10 x 2 Bedroom units, 45 x 2 Bedroom + 2 Bath units, 3 x 3 Bedroom units and 5 x 3 Bedroom Dual Key units.
